      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0349P0_20000504_WH_22'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gareth-thomas-1' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0349P0_20000504_WH_22' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gareth Thomas' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gareth-thomas-1" title="Mr Gareth Thomas">Mr. Thomas</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Will the hon. Gentleman give way?
          </p>
